<plot>Lauren is a young girl caught in a life that delivers no pain and no joy. She lives a life of routine, day after day, comfortably numb. Same meals, same job, same boyfriend, same hobby. When everything in her formulaic life is taken away from her she finds advice in an unlikely friend, a janitor named Clive. Using his advice she attacks the day with a new strategy, and ultimately finds happiness in a world of new possibilities.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?469339</url></doc>
